    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure VANOS. This example features a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission delivering power to a variable M-differential lock. Significant mechanical upkeep is documented, including rod bearing replacement, valve clearance adjustments, and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity. The suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings, providing the telepathic turn-in these cars are known for. While displaying minor aesthetic patina, the powertrain and drivetrain are in excellent health, ready for spirited canyon carving or track-day duty.",
